[00:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'We did it! The BlackBird has taken flight. We are&nbsp;&nbsp; proud to announce the successful maiden&nbsp; flight of our BlackBird demonstrator,&nbsp;&nbsp; marking a major milestone in our mission&nbsp; to revolutionize air mobility. &nbsp; In just 11 months, we went from concept to first&nbsp; flight. Thanks to the dedication, expertise,&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[00:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and relentless spirit of our incredible team,&nbsp; we brought BlackBird to life. For the first&nbsp;&nbsp; time in history an eVTOL with six CycloRotors&nbsp; and MTOW of 340kg has achieved lift-off. &nbsp;'

[00:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'This is not the finish line - it\'s the&nbsp; launchpad. We are now accelerating our&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[01:09] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'flight test program and continuing&nbsp; to refine our CycloRotor technology.&nbsp;&nbsp; We drive progress and redefine&nbsp; what\'s possible in vertical flight.'
